{
  "text": "1. Using the expressions for pressure [CITATION_1] and temperature (3) together with the free energy representation of the first law of thermodynamics (10), we define the thermodynamic Potential (\u2126) or free energy [CITATION_2] corresponding to the horizon-fluid.",
